  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You whisper words of mayhem, as terror spreads within enemy ranks. Choose one creature you can see within range, it must make an intelligence saving throw:</p><ul><li><p><strong>Success</strong>: No effect.</p></li><li><p><strong>Failure</strong>: The affected creature becomes berserk and cannot make hand seals (HS) for the duration. A creature under the effect of this jutsu repeats their saving throw at the end of each of their turns, ending the effect of this jutsu on a success.</p></li><li><p><strong>Critical Failure</strong>: As a failure, but the repeated saving throws are made at disadvantage.</p></li></ul><p><strong>At higher ranks:</strong> For each rank above C-rank, increase this jutsu's cost by +3, and the amount of creatures it can affect by +1.</p>",
